            <answer>
                <p>
                    【分析】注意到函数 <m>y=y(t)</m> 是由方程 <m>y \mathrm{e}^{t}+\mathrm{e}^{t y}=2</m> 所确定的隐函数, 函数 <m>y(x)</m> 由参数方程 <m>\left\{\begin{array}{l}x=t \mathrm{e}^{t}, \\ y=y(t)\end{array}\right.</m> 所确定, 故求 <m>\frac{\mathrm{d} y}{\mathrm{~d} x}</m>, 需先由隐函数求导法则求出 <m>\frac{\mathrm{d} y}{\mathrm{~d} t}</m>, 再由参数方程求导法则求解.</p>

                <p>解: 由已知条件知, 当 <m>x=0</m> 时, <m>t=0, y=1</m>. 对方程 <m>y \mathrm{e}^{t}+\mathrm{e}^{t y}=2</m> 两边关于 <m>t</m> 求导,得
                <me>
                \mathrm{e}^{t} \frac{\mathrm{d} y}{\mathrm{~d} t}+y \mathrm{e}^{t}+\mathrm{e}^{t y}\left(y+t \frac{\mathrm{d} y}{\mathrm{~d} t}\right)=0,
                </me></p>

                <p>解得 <m>\frac{\mathrm{d} y}{\mathrm{~d} t}=-\frac{y\left(\mathrm{e}^{t}+\mathrm{e}^{t y}\right)}{\mathrm{e}^{t}+t \mathrm{e}^{t y}}</m>. 而 <m>\frac{\mathrm{d} x}{\mathrm{~d} t}=\mathrm{e}^{t}+t \mathrm{e}^{t}</m>, 所以
                <me>
                \frac{\mathrm{d} y}{\mathrm{~d} x}=\frac{\frac{\mathrm{d} y}{\mathrm{~d} t}}{\frac{\mathrm{d} x}{\mathrm{~d} t}}=-\frac{y\left(\mathrm{e}^{t}+\mathrm{e}^{t y}\right)}{\left(\mathrm{e}^{t}+t \mathrm{e}^{t y}\right)\left(\mathrm{e}^{t}+t \mathrm{e}^{t}\right)}
                </me></p>

                <p>将 <m>x=0, t=0, y=1</m> 代入, 得 <m>\left.\frac{\mathrm{d} y}{\mathrm{~d} x}\right|_{x=0}=-2</m>.
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

